title: Name me a chat log which you don't hear almost ever. Surprise me :)
body:
Not talking about toxic chat logs, like those you don't expect to hear most of the time, especially weird ones.

One example:

{{champion:14}} : jayce no ult

replies.body: Me kills someone with {{champion:122}} ult enemy laner /all chats dar no ult enemy jg comes and ganks me immediately after he gets dunked as well then a fight follows with them two arguing about me having ult up when he said i didn't in all chat

Fiddlesticks passive kicks in while he's dancing.

"Fiddlesticks.exe has stopped working. Would you like to terminate this program?"

/all referred to my {{champion:6}} when i tp bot: HOW DID YOU SURVIVE


Wait no,i hear that quite a lot.....


Here is one i never hear

{{champion:51}} : GJ Ivern.

Yeah,always flaming the ivern supp (not me,didn't buy him)
